Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.98,0:24:14.98,Sora Eng Titles 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(640,268.75)}After the Typhoon - Visual and Real Images
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:11.38,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time :
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:12.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After the Typhoon
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.50,0:24:14.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Virtual and Real Images
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to leak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:30.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission of Confir... ming the Protection of Circuits for Direct Communication of Orders to Head... quarters under Highly Ur... gent Circum... stances.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:33.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What a long name!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:39.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If failed, every one of us may be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:47.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Under certain conditions, a level-1 warning will be issued and the whole military will be put on alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:52.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right. We have a super-important responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:55.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:57.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:01.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...answering the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:10.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that this phone is connected to Headquarters in the capital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it rung yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:13.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Luckily, it rarely rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:17.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Though we'll be in trouble if it rings,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if it doesn't ring when we really need it to, we'll be in even more trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:27.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why the phone is tested every half year; to see if it's connected properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:28.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:31.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Con... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:33.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remember it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:36.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The command communications line for high-level... What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:41.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission of Confirming the Protection of Circuits for Direct...umm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:48.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission of Confirming the Protection of Circuits for Direct Communication of Orders to Headquarters under Highly Urgent Circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes yes yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let me accept this mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:04:00.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to try to make a call on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:06.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The basic operation is the same as the Takemicaduchi intercom system.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:08.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only difference is the longer distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:13.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wonderful to be able to talk with people that far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:20.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. It feels unbelievable to talk to people that you can't even see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:23.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's nothing if you're used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:27.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately, we don't know when they are going to call today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:29.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still want to accept the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:30.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:31.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:35.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should stick by the phone today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:48.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Private Sorami Kanata of Fortress 1121, Helvetia Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:55.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when the phone call is over, return it to its original position, on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:38.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Feli...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:41.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you are so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:43.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:47.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are you two doing? That's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:49.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The trains are leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:50.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Trains?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:54.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are documents which must be delivered as quickly as possible to Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:57.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-san is coming next week, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we're going to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission of answering the phone really depends on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:03.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:09.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you miss it, the worst-case scenario is that they might assume this place to be under attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:10.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:35.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:37.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:40.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not asleep. I'm not asleep at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:44.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:47.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:49.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not the hangar again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:50.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:52.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:53.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I-I will cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:58.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:02.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Not only Kureha, but you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:06.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever it's my turn to cook, why do you two never want me to do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:10.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you two arrived, I did a lot of cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The taste shouldn't be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:17.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, right, the taste is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the way it looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The taste is very clear. It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:24.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:29.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then today, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:32.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai! It's Naomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:44.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I must be by the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:47.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm a customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:08:01.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to eat sandwiches with bits of cutting board mixed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:07.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is apple cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:11.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it's hand-made by the farmer that delivers our apple juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, this is a relative to our calvados!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:17.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:22.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret has been exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:23.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get two presents for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:33.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er? Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Present?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:38.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be a town gathering for commercial and industrial guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:42.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can benefit from a lot of discounts since giving presents is a tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:43.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:47.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:50.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those girls have been trying so hard to keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:54.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was it exposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:57.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's because... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's the possibility, then someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of talking about that, Naomi-san, do you want to have lunch together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:10.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You mean I'm going to be on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:16.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, according to this week's newspaper, people want to hear a good explanation from the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:17.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,News?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:21.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The meeting for the armistice agreement has turned into a difficult situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:27.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The decisions regarding the amount of reparations and the drawing of the border line are both progressing slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:30.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Drawing things out is always the strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:36.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess what these bosses really want is to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:42.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, because you acted as a Maiden of Flame during the Water Festival, you've got a lot more fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That troubles me. Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:51.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, it seems that I have to go out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:55.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am already a Maiden of the Fortress in body and soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:57.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will perform the mission by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:00.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I will leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, please try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:11.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry that it's a used copy of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:14.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... for the trumpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:18.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful, beautiful, beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:19.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:23.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are getting a lot better at horns!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:26.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a reward for practicing hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you have this, you won't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:43.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, this is C, D, E, F, G...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:46.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:05.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer is already over, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:15.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:22.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I drink too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:31.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:34.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining! The laundry will get wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:40.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The courtyard is a high-level war-zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:51.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-na-ta, let's play~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:53.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-e-s!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:56.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-na-ta, let's play~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:15.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. I'm so glad the laundry is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really great...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:21.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked for you to help me suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:26.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind it, we were the ones who came to visit you all of a sudden. Really sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:31.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We must return to Treize, so we are here to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:34.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's really kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:37.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't really need to say goodbye to the military at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:39.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that, Seiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:48.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This kid isn't polite to the people from the base, so please accept my apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:52.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Rio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:57.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}TL note: Yes... this priest has color blindness... so does Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:56.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one with black hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to see... uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This book is... yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:09.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A book about trumpets. I got it from Rio-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:11.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:12.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:18.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, nothing. Excuse me. I'm talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:20.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, are you watching the place by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:21.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:32.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm in the middle of the Confirming the Protection of Circuits for Direct Communication of Orders to the Headquarters under Highly Urgent Circumstances mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:39.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that is, waiting for this thing to ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:45.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this will be my first time using it. I'm a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:49.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I answer it correctly? Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:51.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:59.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, is Yumina-san also gone for the gathering of guilds?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:05.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... she went to receive the endowments from everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:11.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:12.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:13.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-kun, please drink some too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:18.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drink it, but I won't be conciliated by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:26.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do anything for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:30.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san, you kids know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:31.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a telephone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:42.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:44.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. A telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:49.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids like them, so I sometimes make some for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Seiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:51.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a telephone... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:01.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Hello~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:03.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Great, Seiya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:08.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong. You should say "hello" first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is how you make phone calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He... Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:16.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. It's so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:19.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really, really can hear your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:22.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to practice like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:22.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:25.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:26.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:28.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:35.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Private Sorami Kanata of Fortress 1121, Helvetia Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. It's not so tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:40.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's so kind of you to call me on the phone at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:42.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. It's not so tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:45.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, birdie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:55.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The telephone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:32.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Is the priest and my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:54.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:59.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:06.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are here to show your appreciation and apologize for all the things that happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:09.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you are playing and causing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that include me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:22.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no problem. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:25.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, your clothes are wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. Spare clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:33.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate does exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:44.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You look radiant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:51.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, thank you Yumina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:53.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will return it to you after it's washed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:55.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:59.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too big for the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:03.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I know any other people who it'd fit better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:08.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still gonna play with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-kun, you too. Please come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:14.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:24.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am free, I'll come and play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:27.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:30.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We wish God bestows a lot of happiness upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:33.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:40.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let me get everything back in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:44.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot. Toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:21.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to leak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:16.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... hurry... hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:23.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. What's with that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:25.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong with you, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:28.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:32.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:33.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's... wrong, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:36.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... hold... any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to leak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:43.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go now! Or you'll get sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She has been holding it in all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:51.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I say that it's obedient, or just stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:00.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:03.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:05.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even move an inch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:13.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These people... What terrible timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:21.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. This is Staff-Sergeant Rio Kazumiya of Fortress 1121, Helvetia Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:24.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:30.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they were confirming your circuits. Though they said "It's useless!"...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:33.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm not escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:38.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. You can never forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:47.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Please, save the country. Save Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:56.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan, I can't believe you've been sleeping since morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:59.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. I can sleep well on the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:01.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can that be!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:05.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're bac... {\alpha&HFF&}Wow! What a lovely dress, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:10.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're bac... Wow! What a lovely dress, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:13.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... What are you two doing in the corridor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.48,0:22:16.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata has tripped. She can't stand back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:17.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You got hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.39,0:22:20.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:26.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. I have to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:28.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My spoiled little child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:30.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.63,0:22:33.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.34,0:22:36.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
